        </li>

        <li class="two">
            <h5>SignalR</h5>
            SignalR is Real-Time Communications library for the web
            <a href="http://signalr.net/">Learn more…</a>
        </li>

        <li class="three">
            <h5>Windows Azure</h5>
            Windows Azure is Microsofts Cloud Hosting Solution
            <a href="http://www.windowsazure.com/">Learn more…</a>
        </li>
    </ol>
</article>

